race.comment: FRISKEE FROG (9) unlucky not to have a few more wins on the CV, and capable of going one better today. Strong through the line on the quick backup when second over 1180m at Gundagai. Gets weight relief again and can get across from the sticky draw. SUNRISE RIDGE (16) impressive return from the lengthy break when a slick Maiden winner over 1000m at this track. Only has to hold that form to take a hand in the finish. CIAO BELLA MIA (14) brings a solid set of figures to this contest but poorly drawn. Warmed up late when a tough fourth over 1200m at Nowra. Hard fit now and don't dismiss. ALESUND (5) chasing his third win in four starts and not to be overlooked despite the rise in grade. Solid win here last start and hard to ignore in this type of form.
